== 假想机制 ==
在磁场下暴露的时间、强度、升降率、变化速度以及水平或垂直于流体的方向，被各个结论认为对结果至关重要。 <ref name="Chaplin">{{Cite web|title=Descaling of Water|url=http://www1.lsbu.ac.uk/water/descal.html#212|accessdate=2012-03-26|author=Chaplin|date=2011-07-26|first=M.|work=Water Structure and Science|publisher=[[London_South_Bank_University|London South Bank University]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527094356/http://www.lsbu.ac.uk/water/descal.html#212|archivedate=2012-05-27}}</ref>磁化水处理的支持者Klaus Kronenberg提出，溶质[[石灰|石灰]]分子的形状会受到强磁场的影响，导致它们沉淀为球形或圆形晶体，而非沉积为硬质晶体的片状。 <ref>
{{Cite web|title=Interview of Klaus Kronenberg, Ph. D|url=http://www.gmxinternational.com/facts/interview/05.htm|accessdate=2012-03-26|publisher=GMX International|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222171300/http://www.gmxinternational.com/facts/interview/05.htm|archivedate=2012-02-22}}</ref>[[克蘭菲爾德大學|克蘭菲爾德大學]]水科学学院的西蒙·帕森斯（Simon Parsons）提出，磁场会减少小颗粒的表面电荷，从而按比例增加流动时凝结为大颗粒而非沉积的趋势。但1996年[[勞倫斯利佛摩國家實驗室|勞倫斯利佛摩國家實驗室]]进行的一项内部研究中发现，磁化水处理系统中，沉积水垢的主要晶体结构没有差异。 <ref name="Krauter1996">
{{Cite journal|title=Test of a Magnetic Device for Amelioration of Scale Formation at Treatment Facility D|url=http://www.osti.gov/bridge/servlets/purl/567404-bQ4DwB/webviewable/567404.pdf|last=Krauter|first=PW|last2=Harrar|first2=JE|journal=Internal Report|publisher=[[Lawrence_Livermore_National_Laboratory|Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory]]|accessdate=2009-12-11|issue=|doi=10.2172/567404|year=1996|volume=|pages=|osti=567404|last3=Orloff|first3=SP|last4=Bahowick|first4=SM}}</ref>

Liu<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Surface Modification and Planar Defects of Calcium Carbonates by Magnetic Water Treatment|last=Liu|first=C. Z.|last2=Lin|first2=C. H.|journal=Nanoscale Research Letters|issue=12|doi=10.1007/s11671-010-9736-5|year=2010|volume=5|pages=1982–1991|bibcode=2010NRL.....5.1982L|pmc=2991221|pmid=21170405|last3=Yeh|first3=M. S.|last4=Chao|first4=Y. M.|last5=Shen|first5=P}}</ref>、Coey和Cass在2010年和2000年发表的研究报告中指出，磁化处理使包含矿物质的水更利于形成更易溶解的碳酸钙形式（[[霰石|霰石]]而非[[方解石|方解石]]）。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Magnetic water treatment|url=http://www.ecaa.ntu.edu.tw/weifang/water/Magnetic%20water%20treatment.pdf|last=Coey|first=JMD|last2=Cass|first2=S|journal=[[Journal_of_Magnetism_and_Magnetic_Materials|Journal of Magnetism and Magnetic Materials]]|issue=1–3|doi=10.1016/S0304-8853(99)00648-4|year=2000|volume=209|pages=71–74|bibcode=2000JMMM..209...71C|pmc=|pmid=|access-date=2020-11-17|archive-date=2011-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409160123/http://www.ecaa.ntu.edu.tw/weifang/water/Magnetic%20water%20treatment.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 管材 ===
电磁处理的效果依赖于管道特性。影响幅度取决于管道的电导率和表面粗糙度。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Effect of magnetic water treatment on calcium carbonate precipitation: Influence of the pipe material|last=Alimi|first=F.|last2=Tlili|first2=M. M.|journal=Chemical Engineering and Processing: Process Intensification|issue=8|doi=10.1016/j.cep.2009.06.008|year=2009|volume=48|pages=1327|pmc=|pmid=|last3=Amor|first3=M. B.|last4=Maurin|first4=G.|last5=Gabrielli|first5=C.}}</ref>

